    "description": "On July 2nd, 1937 the U.S. Coast Guard cutter Itasca received the last recorded words of Amelia Earhart. She was never seen or heard of again. Her Lockheed E-10 was lost with her. No wreckage or any fragments were ever found despite a 250,000 square mile search the size of Texas being conducted by the United States Navy.<br>On July 2nd 1937, Amelia Earhart and her plane disappeared forever.  <br><br><i>“We are on the line 157-337 flying north and south.”</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149230/extras/dca5ae1fec20f8009dda2771db34e328.poster.avif?t=1666453676\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149230/extras/dca5ae1fec20f8009dda2771db34e328.webm?t=1666453676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149230/extras/dca5ae1fec20f8009dda2771db34e328.mp4?t=1666453676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Assuming the identity of Fred Noonan, Alex is about to become the navigator of the doomed flight that was supposed to be a monumental moment in history as Amelia Earhart attempted to be the first woman to fly around the world, but which instead turned to tragedy. <br><br>Aboard the plane during its fateful flight, Alex might find finally the answers of what happened. But he's going to have to convince the world that he's Fred Noonan first..<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149230/extras/246e05fb92ea1fd41af5212d471739e0.poster.avif?t=1666453676\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149230/extras/246e05fb92ea1fd41af5212d471739e0.webm?t=1666453676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149230/extras/246e05fb92ea1fd41af5212d471739e0.mp4?t=1666453676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As suspicions escalate can Alex maintain his cover or will Amelia uncover the deception? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149230/extras/b88aed8e4a63b428a6f7142b40a077c7.poster.avif?t=1666453676\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149230/extras/b88aed8e4a63b428a6f7142b40a077c7.webm?t=1666453676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149230/extras/b88aed8e4a63b428a6f7142b40a077c7.mp4?t=1666453676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And even if Alex can convince everyone, he still has to figure out how to become a navigator. <br>Recreate the real-life flight route and confront whatever danger lurks ahead..",
